creator: Education Jack Media
descriptionHtml:
Right from understanding the topics to clearing the exam, we offer you a one-stop solution for all your learning needs. Now learn with us, uninterrupted from the safety of your home.

Our app is the go-to solution for students across the country with a simple user interface, design, and exciting features.
åWhy study with us? Want to know what all you will get? 🤔

🎦 Interactive live classes
Now, let’s recreate our physical experiences through our state-of-the-art live classes interface where multiple students can study together.
- Periodical live classes to ensure you clear your exams
- Raise your hand feature to solve individual queries

📚 Course material
- Get access to the course, notes, and other study material on-the-go
- Regularly updated content

📝 Tests and performance reports
- Get online tests and exams
- Track your performance, test scores & rank from time to time.

❓ Ask every doubt
- Clearing doubts has never been easier. Ask your doubts by just clicking a screenshot/photo of the question and uploading it. We’ll ensure that all your doubts are clarified.
- Clear your doubts on the go through our mobile app

🏆Proven record of excellence:
- We have been part of the market for a long time now and we have helped multiple candidates clear their exams.
- Excellence has always been our motto, and the only thing that will never change is our motto.

⏰ Reminders and notifications for batches and sessions
- Get notifications about new courses, sessions and updates. No more worrying about missed classes, sessions, etc. because we only want you to focus on your studies.
- Get announcements around exam dates/special classes/ special events etc.

📜 Assignment submission
- Practice makes a student perfect. Get regular online assignments so that you can become perfect.
- Submit your assignments online and we will help you in evaluating your performance

💻 Anytime access
- Watch our classes, live or recorded, anytime from any of your devices.
🤝 Parent-Teacher discussion
- Parents can download the app and connect with teachers & track their ward’s performance
- Parents can easily chat with the teacher in case of any query

💸 Payments and fees
- Easy fees submission with 100% safe and secure payment options
Online fee payment option for ease

🏆 Compete within groups
- Compete within groups and with peers who are stuying
- Get to see your comparative score as compared to peer students

🪧 Ads Free
- No ads for a seamless studying experience

🛡️Safe and secure
- Safety of your data i.e. phone number, email address, etc. is of utmost importance
- We never use student data for any kind of advertisement

An online platform for studying most efficiently and transparently. Download now !!

descriptionShort: Connect with Dr. Monica Jain in an efficient and transparent manner
title: Dr. Monica Jain

creator: Education Jack Media
descriptionHtml:
The whole purpose of education is to turn mirrors into windows.

At Dr. Monica Jain, we strive to work towards the mental and academic growth of every learner, in consideration with their interests, goals and aptitude.

Dr. Monica Jain encourages all to turn their dreams into reality; their nightmares to strengths! Be it scary Chemistry; For everything, we got your back!

We believe in making learning experiences smooth and easy for all. Having hands-on experience with Chemistry for 10th/ 11th/ 12th /IIT JEE/ NEET coaching sessions, we employ the most appropriate and productive methodologies. By giving careful attention to every subject and each topic, our students acquire knowledge along with an enhanced skill set.

USP :
● Explained all Chemistry Topics & Concepts in v. simple and easy way.
● A lot of free study material is available.
● Affordable Courses.
● Courses are having Videos along with pdfs. of Study material.
● The course is having Test series also for practice & better understanding.
●

🏆Proven record of excellence:
● Imparting Education for 10+ Years
● 7K+ Students educated.


Why study with us? Want to know what all you will get?🤔

● 🎦 Interactive live classes-Let’s recreate our physical experiences now through our state-of-the-art live classes interface where multiple students can study, together. It's not only about asking doubts but comprehensive discussions too!

● ❓ Ask every doubt-Clearing doubts has never been easier. Ask your doubts by just clicking a screenshot/photo of the question and uploading it. We’ll ensure that all your doubts are clarified.

● 🤝 Parent-Teacher discussion-Parents can download the app and connect with teachers & track their ward’s performance.

● 📝 Tests and performance reports-Enables students to take tests and get easy access to their performance in the form of interactive reports.

● 📚 Course material-Different types of courses have been designed according to the syllabus and needs of students. Never miss out on new courses!!

● Ads Free- No ads for seamless studying experience

● 💻 Anytime access-You can access your application anytime and from anywhere.

● 🔐Safe and secure- Safety of your data i.e. phone number, email address, etc. is of utmost importance
● This app also emphasizes 'Learning by doing' (a famous practical approach by Dewey).

All this is now made available to you simply through the application.Join the league of toppers just by downloading Mobile App and get started now!


Follow us :

● Instagram: https://instagram.com/chemistry_pathshala_drmonica?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=
● Email: monicajain210967@gmail.com
